          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1650451798150-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, peel and roughly dice the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Deseed the <strong>pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and dice</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
